## 🔥 Pattern Analysis: What's Winning in 2026

### Category Distribution

```
AI Agents / Agentic Workflows     ████████████████░░░░░  32%
Healthcare / Mental Health Equity  ██████████████░░░░░░░  28%
Climate / Sustainability / Energy  ████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░  15%
Agriculture / Food / Rural Dev     ██████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  12%
Cybersecurity / Defense            ████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░   7%
Web3 / Blockchain                  ███░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░   6%
```

### What Changed from 2024-2025 → 2026

| Dimension | 2024-2025 | 2026 | Shift |
|-----------|-----------|------|-------|
| **AI Focus** | Chatbots, RAG, single-agent | Multi-agent orchestration, AI governance, AI safety | From "can AI do this?" to "can we trust AI doing this?" |
| **Healthcare** | Basic symptom checkers, telemedicine | Mental health parity, clinician burnout, cognitive dignity, health equity | From "access" to "equity and quality" |
| **Sustainability** | Carbon calculators, monitoring | Infrastructure-level adaptation, green AI, construction material reuse | From "measuring" to "adapting and building" |
| **Accessibility** | Translation apps, screen readers | Physical assistive devices (smart canes, wearables), cognitive load management | From "digital accessibility" to "physical + cognitive accessibility" |
| **Agriculture** | Crop monitoring dashboards | Farmer burnout reduction, open-source precision ag, biodiversity protection | From "yield optimization" to "farmer wellbeing + ecosystem health" |
| **Defense** | Cybersecurity tools | Multi-domain sensor fusion, airspace protection, AI agent security | From "defense of data" to "defense of systems" |

